welcome_message_body: Welcome to Pasir Gudang, where the vibrant mix of industry and natural beauty creates a unique charm. Explore our bustling port city and discover our rich cultural heritage, delicious cuisine, and stunning natural landscapes. Enjoy your stay and immerse yourself in all that Pasir Gudang has to offer!
